steps.title: Project Navigation
steps.description: Use the sidebar to switch between different sections of your project, like your Dashboard or Locations.

steps.title: Welcome to Character Vault
steps.description: This is where you define your cast! The AI uses these character references to maintain consistency across your stories.

steps.title: Edit or Delete
steps.description: Hover over a card to reveal options to edit character details or remove them from your vault.

steps.title: Add New Characters
steps.description: Click here to create a new character. You can upload an image and add a description to define their personality.
